node.text:
FILA is celebrating its 110th Anniversary in 2021. To honor its iconic heritage, the brand has partnered with British stylist and cultural curator Katie Grand (@kegrand) to reinterpret a series of classic styles from the FILA archives housed in Biella, Italy. 

The special collection focuses on a variety of themes that explore the brand’s rich history in sport: Tennis, Mountain, Water, Aerobics, Basketball, Golf and Motosports. The pieces selected, chosen for their historical value and beauty, have been reissued and redesigned with a modern update.

The 110th Anniversary Collection is presented through a short film, created by Katie Grand and Steve Mackey and directed by Mackey.

#FILA110
